Where are you?

1:25:45.265 --> 1:25:47.225
KAREN:
I'm at Mother's.

1:25:47.392 --> 1:25:49.727
I'm going to stay a few days.

1:25:49.895 --> 1:25:52.730
I'll stay with you on the phone here.

1:25:53.732 --> 1:25:56.317
Until we work this thing out.

1:26:04.409 --> 1:26:06.577
