1:26:08.247 --> 1:26:13.501
Starts here at A-32,
goes up to plus five. ..

1:26:13.669 --> 1:26:17.088
...and then stops here at JO-6.

1:26:21.301 --> 1:26:23.678
Karen, what's done is done.

