together before.

1:29:09.928 --> 1:29:11.887
You've got a deal, Mike.

1:29:12.055 --> 1:29:14.432
Why don't you tell me a story?

1:29:15.392 --> 1:29:17.601
You know, the way we used to.

1:29:17.769 --> 1:29:19.854
KAREN:
A story about us.

1:29:28.864 --> 1:29:32.241
-My work is my life.
-We're working for them. It's not up to me.

1:29:40.417 --> 1:29:43.252
