1:31:13.718 --> 1:31:15.719
[BEEPING]

1:31:30.235 --> 1:31:33.821
-Bill! You gotta open up!
MAN: Hold on, hold on.

1:31:33.989 --> 1:31:37.241
The whole place is up for grabs.
Someone bypassed the control system.

1:31:37.409 --> 1:31:39.743
