1:34:09.728 --> 1:34:13.522
-And that should do it.
-Okay.

1:35:18.463 --> 1:35:21.131
-At that time, do that. Watches the same?
-Right.

1:35:21.299 --> 1:35:22.383
Thanks, you guys.

1:35:22.550 --> 1:35:24.927
-I love it.
-Take care.

1:35:30.141 --> 1:35:32.101
MAN:
It won't open.

1:35:32.268 --> 1:35:34.853
Here, move. Get out of the way.

1:35:45.073 --> 1:35:46.532
Shit.

1:35:47.158 --> 1:35:51.954
I bet they're making phone contact through
the lab computer. Have them run a trace.

1:35:52.789 --> 1:35:53.872
Doug.

1:35:54.457 --> 1:35:55.499
